essdate=2 June 2016}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|35||0||7||1||2||0||11{{efn|Eight appearances and one goal in UEFA Champions League, three appearances in UEFA Europa League}}||1||colspan=2|\u2014||55||2\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 Manchester United F.C. season|2016\u201317]]<ref name=sb1617>{{soccerbase season|51128|2016|accessdate=16 July 2017}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|18||1||4||1||4||0||10{{efn|name=UEL}}||0||0||0||36||2\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Manchester United F.C. season|2017\u201318]]<ref name=sb1718>{{soccerbase season|51128|2017|accessdate=28 May 2018}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|29||4||5||0||3||0||8{{efn|name=UCL}}||0||1{{efn|name=USC|Appearance in [[UEFA Super Cup]]}}||0||46||4\n|-\n|[[2018\u201319 Manchester United F.C. season|2018\u201319]]<ref name=sb1819>{{soccerbase season|51128|2018|accessdate=14 July 2019}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|24||1||2||0||0||0||8{{efn|name=UCL}}||0||colspan=2|\u2014||34||1\n|-\n|[[2019\u201320 Manchester United F.C. season|2019\u201320]]<ref name=sb1920>{{soccerbase season|51128|2019|accessdate=30 August 2019}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|0||0||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!206||12||34||2||17||1||62||2||4||1||323||18\n|-\n|[[A.S. Roma|Roma]] (loan)\n|[[2019\u201320 A.S. Roma season|2019\u201320]]<ref name=Soccerway>{{cite web |url=https://uk.soccerway.com/players/chris-smalling/79474/ |title=C. Smalling: Summary |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=3 March 2020}}</ref>\n|[[Serie A]]\n|21||2||2||0||colspan=2|\u2014||5{{efn|name=UEL}}||0||colspan=2|\u2014||28||2\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!240||14||37||2||18||1||71||2||4||1||370||20\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 10 June 2017}}<ref name=NFT>{{NFT player |pid=40554 |name=Smalling, Chris |accessdate=30 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan