amed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=April 19, 2020}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|2|artist=Drake|song=Toosie Slide|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 17, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand ([[Recorded Music NZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4848|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=April 20, 2020|accessdate=April 18, 2020}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Norway ([[VG-lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2020-16/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 16, 2020|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|13|date=20200417|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 18, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Singapore ([[Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|RIAS]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|title=RIAS International Top Charts Week 15|publisher=Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417101348/https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|archive-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n{{single chart|Slovakdigital|6|year=2020|week=15|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 15, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Spain ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|PROMUSICAE]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elportaldemusica.es/lists/top-100-canciones/2020/15|title=Top 100 Canciones: Semana 15|publisher=[[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a]]|accessdate=April 16, 2020}}</ref>\n| 45\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Sweden ([[Sverigetopplistan]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2020&dspp=16|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 16|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n| 3\n|-\n{{single chart|Switzerland|3|artist=Drake|song=Toosie Slide|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 13, 2020}}\n|-\n{{sing